</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="dramatis personae">
<PB REF="034381_0143_0FFF0FDCD9891FE8">
<LIST>
<HEAD>CHARACTERS.</HEAD>
<ITEM>Squire Aubrey, Proprietor of the Manor</ITEM>
<ITEM>Colonel Ne&s;bit,</ITEM>
<ITEM><LIST>
<ITEM>Lady Aubrey,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Mi&s;s Ne&s;bit,</ITEM>
</LIST> His Daughters.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Robert, An old Pea&s;ant.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Lucetta, His Daughter.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Phillip, Married to Lucetta.</ITEM>
